summary: I’m convinced when Harry doesn’t have someone telling him precisely what to wear he stands in his closet with his arms out,...
body: I’m convinced when Harry doesn’t have someone telling him precisely what to wear he stands in his closet with his arms out, spinning around, and wearing whatever snags on his ginormous hands and falls to the floor. Doesn’t even look. Just shoves it on and goes.

summary: Arriving in Cabo, Harry carried a pink Outdoor Voices tote bag. Each Outdoor Voices purchase comes in a canvas tote, branded...
caption:
Arriving in Cabo, Harry carried a pink Outdoor Voices tote bag. Each Outdoor Voices purchase comes in a canvas tote, branded with a company slogan, which is periodically updated in new styles and colors. The bags on their own usually aren’t available for purchase. Harry’s bag says ‘Outdoor Voices - Technical Apparel for Recreation on one side and ‘Los Angeles’ on the other. 

Outdoor Voices canvas tote bag ($15)
worn with Vans Classic Tumble Old Skool Trainers and Gucci sunglasses
